reviewText: It brought back my childhood. Thanks. :-D
mr magoo is just as i remembered him when i was young. our grandchildren laugh out loud while watching the video in the car, even though they had never previously heard of mr magoo.
We've thoroughly enjoyed the trip down nostalgic lane with this dvd.  The quality is great - no problems whatsoever.
It was a hit with my African brothers from Ghana, who had never seen the show before, & a funny reminder to me why I loved it as a kid.
